name: RTCOutboundRtpStreamStats.qpSum
description: The qpSum property of the RTCOutboundRtpStreamStats dictionary is a value generated by adding the Quantization Parameter (QP) values for every frame this sender has produced to date on the video track corresponding to this RTCOutboundRtpStreamStats object.
